data.description: This charming home offers a true outdoor entertaining experience w/ a multi-level travertine patio approx. 2500sf , a pebble tec play pool, Built in BBQ, & a cozy Fireplace w/ Banco seating. Fully landscaped w/auto watering, easy care landscaping. 4 stall Mare motel w/turnout area & room to expanded. Enjoy the endless mountain views from the rooftop deck. Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, newer Viking fridge, & a large island w/ breakfast bar opens to the great room living space. Entertain in the formal living room/dining room that features large sliding doors to enjoy all the views! Yard is completely fenced to protect pets from predators & preserve privacy. This home has it all & only minutes from the Tonto National Forest, hiking, biking, off-roading, horseback riding.. golfing, restaurants & the Verde River Recreational area. Shared Well & short distance off paved road!
